  \subsection boxes_models_box Box

  | Field           | Type    | Description      |
  |-----------------|---------|------------------|
  | id              | integer | Primary key, ID of the box    |
  | user_id         | integer | References to the user account to which the box is attached |
  | type            | string  | Type of the box (Image, Collection, Presentation, etc.) |
  | position        | integer | Position within the sequence of boxes |
  | expanded        | boolean | Is the box display in an expanded view? |
  | per_page        | integer | Available options for the nof. items to display per expanded box |
  | box_per_page | integer | nof. items to display per expanded box |
  | order | string | Available options for the metadata field by which the entries are ordered |
  | box_order | string | Metadata field by which the entries are ordered |
  | direction | string | Available options for ordering the items inside the box |
  | box_direction | string | Direction in which the items are ordered inside the box |
  | image_id | integer | ID of the image |
  | collection_id | integer | ID of the image collection |
  | presentation_id | integer | ID of the presentation |

